column5: Hello!  Nice to see this site still operating!  My last username here was urbanangler. I'm 23 now and for past 3,4 years I've been working, lived at a couple address, and had other things take up my time such as work and gf, and dog. Well I'm back and eager to get back into fishing.  I recognize old members from the past, nice to see yall!
Remember your name well.  Well come back.
Hey!  Welcome back!  Brian B would have been Misfish when you were here last.
Hey! Welcome back! Brian B would have been Misfish when you were here last.  There goes my cover. Thanks Cliff.  Yes,is I.
Thanks Brian B aka misfish, thanks ccmt, i remember you both well, nice to see yall
Yep Welcome back! Even tho I haven't been here much either. Haven't been out chasing carp lately either.
Hey dsn, you and I both, I'm looking forward to dusting off my equipment
Welcome Back! I haven't left here just hiding in the shadows.
my equipment is collecting dust. Been busy, haven't been out for many moons. Found a new hobby.
